com.pom.crimson.pages

Class HomePage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pom.crimson.base.BaseFixture
      • com.pom.crimson.base.BasePage
        • com.pom.crimson.pages.HomePage

  • public class HomePage
extends BasePage
    When user logs in to app, Home page is displayed.
    User can view recommended content, daily tips and navigate to various other pages like Live Events,Talk to doctor nurse, Moments log etc from home page. This page class contains MobileElements on this page and functions to simulate interactions with these elements.
    Author:
    Jaspreet Kaur Chagger, Sivaprakash.Selvaraj, Indirani
